  "challengeEducation01Desc": "Since 2026, the 13th AVS pension increases your annual pension. Discover what this means concretely for you.",
  "challengeEducation01Title": "Read the article on the 13th AVS pension",
  "challengeEducation02Desc": "The LPP conversion rate of 6.8% only applies to the minimum. Your fund may have a different rate for the supra-mandatory portion.",
  "challengeEducation02Title": "Understand the difference between minimum and supra-mandatory conversion rates",
  "challengeEducation03Desc": "The AVS is a pay-as-you-go system: working people fund retirees. Understand the basics of your future pension.",
  "challengeEducation03Title": "Discover how the 1st pillar works",
  "challengeEducation04Desc": "AVS + LPP + 3a: each pillar has its role. Understand how they complement each other for your retirement.",
  "challengeEducation04Title": "Understand the 3-pillar system",
  "challengeEducation05Desc": "The replacement rate measures the ratio between your pension and your last salary. The common target is 60-80%.",
  "challengeEducation05Title": "Explore the concept of replacement rate",
  "challengeEducation06Desc": "LPP contributions increase with age: 7%, 10%, 15%, 18%. Check which bracket you are in.",
  "challengeEducation06Title": "Understand LPP contributions by age bracket",
  "challengeEducation07Desc": "In cohabitation, you do not have the same inheritance rights as a married person. Check the necessary protections.",
  "challengeEducation07Title": "Discover the financial consequences of cohabitation",
  "challengeEducation08Desc": "Women receive on average 37% less pension. Understand the causes and possible solutions.",
  "challengeEducation08Title": "Understand the impact of the gender gap on retirement",
  "challengeEpargne01Desc": "Even a small amount counts: CHF 50 per week is CHF 2,600 per year. The hardest part is starting.",
  "challengeEpargne01Title": "Set aside CHF 50 this week",
  "challengeEpargne02Desc": "The 3a ceiling for employees is CHF 7,258 per year. Check how much you have already contributed this year.",
  "challengeEpargne02Title": "Check your 3a balance vs the ceiling",
  "challengeEpargne03Desc": "An LPP buyback is tax-deductible. Simulate the impact of a CHF 5,000 buyback on your pension and taxes.",
  "challengeEpargne03Title": "Simulate an LPP buyback of CHF 5,000",
  "challengeEpargne04Desc": "3a contributions are annual: if you haven't reached the maximum yet, there may still be time.",
  "challengeEpargne04Title": "Check whether you can still contribute to 3a this year",
  "challengeEpargne05Desc": "Not all 3a accounts are equal. Compare your account returns with the simulator.",
  "challengeEpargne05Title": "Compare the returns on your 3a accounts",
  "challengeEpargne06Desc": "A 1% return with 1.5% inflation is a negative real return. Check your situation.",
  "challengeEpargne06Title": "Calculate the real return on your 3a after inflation",
  "challengeEpargne07Desc": "Withdrawing your 3a over several years can reduce tax. Simulate the staggered withdrawal strategy.",
  "challengeEpargne07Title": "Simulate a staggered withdrawal from your 3a accounts",
  "challengeEpargne08Desc": "Since 2025, you can make up years without contributions. Check whether you are eligible for retroactive 3a.",
  "challengeEpargne08Title": "Check whether you can contribute retroactively to 3a",
  "challengeEpargne09Desc": "When changing jobs, your LPP capital is transferred to a vested benefits account. Check that nothing was forgotten.",
